title: How To Get Motivated to Lose Weight
itunes:title: How To Get Motivated to Lose Weight
description:
Get the Free Course here:
https://phit.click/freecourse

 

In this live I teach you all the ways we like to find motivation and why that's TERRIBLE.

Most of us have no idea how to get motivated and that's because we are looking in the wrong places.

Today you will learn the three keys to getting yourself motivated to lose weight.

Here's a hint: The first step is getting off your couch.
